{"tid":93851,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[宵夜]大家食四洲蝦餅果陣有無試過塊餅痴住左個嘴","createTime":"2017-01-24T17:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T09:37:24.000Z","uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d558c1724ad6164bf9b949f77439fd155b1de22c","tid":93851,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2F8V9eV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2F8V9eV.jpg&h=911bba72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/013808_b24a406a409e29dde6eb53d12fd89ac1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F013808_b24a406a409e29dde6eb53d12fd89ac1.jpg&h=889defd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太耐無食 買左包做宵夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但第一啖食落去就成塊餅痴住左個嘴唇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搣極都搣唔開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一搣開果下好似搣爛埋我個嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151c18fece7e71018d5ad0358e731506c2b0ed30","tid":93851,"uid":67996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:43:36.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />格硬撕落黎<br />\n連血一齊食"},{"pid":"dd82429a51e6e51babe7feb2f6bea3d71c3335cb","tid":93851,"uid":29863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:44:23.000Z","msg":"試過痴到甩埋嘴脣皮 痛撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBut原味先係王道"},{"pid":"32b8067f4310efc88fa445d1f55daf7980aaade0","tid":93851,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過痴到甩埋嘴脣皮 痛撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBut原味先係王道</blockquote><br />\n原味都會痴住個嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl